Properties.Caption: Просмотр чеков по заключениям на возврат
Properties.Tag: Select [K_BD].[CBD] As [Код бюджета], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Номер чека], [DOC].[DDOC] As [Дата приема], [DOC_DO].[DDO] As [Дата выдачи], [DOC_1].[CDOC] As [Заключение], [DOC_1].[DU_OT] As [Дата казначейства], [DOC_1].[D_RETURN] As [Дата приостановки], [DOC].[D_RETURN] As [Дата аннулирования], Sum([ZF_D_ZNI].[SUMM]) As [Сумма] From (((((((((((([DOC] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC_DOC] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[DOCID]=[DOC_DOC].[DOCID] And [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID]=[DOC].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [ZF_D_ZNI] With (NoLock) On ([DOC_DOC].[DOCID_PARENT]=[ZF_D_ZNI].[DOCID] And [DOC_DOC].[K_TDID_PARENT]=[ZF_D_ZNI].[K_TDID])) Inner Join [K_LS] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_D_ZNI].[K_LSID]=[K_LS].[K_LSID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_LS].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [DOC] As [DOC_1] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_D_ZNI].[DOCID]=[DOC_1].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_TS] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_D_ZNI].[K_TSID]=[K_TS].[K_TSID])) Inner Join [K_TS_K_UL_ROLE] With (NoLock) On ([K_TS].[K_TSID]=[K_TS_K_UL_ROLE].[K_TSID] And [K_TS_K_UL_ROLE].[K_ROLEID]=21)) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_1] With (NoLock) On ([K_TS_K_UL_ROLE].[K_ULID]=[K_UL_1].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL_ROLE] With (NoLock) On ([K_TS_K_UL_ROLE].[K_ULID]=[K_UL_ROLE].[K_ULID] And [K_UL_ROLE].[K_ROLEID]=21)) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_ROLE] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_ROLE].[K_UL_ROLEID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_ROLE].[K_UL_ROLEID])) Left Join [DOC_DO] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[DOCID]=[DOC_DO].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Where [DOC].[K_TDID]=45 And [Apps_Groups_K_UL_ROLE].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And [DOC].[FLAGS] / 32 Mod 2<>0 And |0 Group by [K_BD].[CBD], [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DDOC], [DOC_DO].[DDO], [DOC_1].[CDOC], [DOC_1].[DU_OT], [DOC_1].[D_RETURN], [DOC].[D_RETURN] Order by |1
